<topic id="contribute_options_page_from_plugin">
    <title>Contributing a Custom Preferences Page</title>
    <body>
        <p>There is a specific plugin extension type that can be used to contribute a <xref
        href="../topics/optionpage-plugin.dita">custom preferences page</xref> to the
        <b>Preferences</b> dialog box in <ph keyref="product"/>. An example of how such a page is
      implemented can be found in this sample plugin: <xref
        href="https://github.com/oxygenxml/oxygen-dita-prolog-updater/blob/master/src/main/java/com/oxygenxml/prolog/updater/view/PrologOptionPage.java"
        format="java" scope="external"/>.</p>
    </body>
